children.text:
Action.new("Append to pattern") { |obj, ch|
        obj.buffer << ch.chr
        obj.buffer_changed
      }

Action.new("Delete Prev Char") { |obj, ch|
        # backspace
        buff = obj.buffer
        buff = buff[0..-2] unless buff == ""
        obj.set_buffer buff
      }
